         <div class="home__about u-flex-row">
         <div class="u-flex-row__block">
            <img src="https://www.brandprotectiongroup.org/assets/images/home-who-we-are.jpg" alt="Who We Are" class="u-img-responsive">
         </div>
         <div class="u-flex-row__block">
            <div class="home__about-content">
               <span class="home__about-title">Brand Protection Group</span>
               <p>Brand Protection Group - Lebanon is an association of leading local, regional and international manufacturers and distributors established in 2003, to confront the phenomenon of counterfeiting, smuggling and copying all types of products, in particular consumer products in Lebanon.</p>

<p>The core objective is to protect intellectual property rights and to preserve the rights of the consumer against fraud and illicit competition.</p>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
      
   <div class="home__warning" id="get-involved">
      If you suspect a product to be counterfeit, you may:
