                     <div class="u-two-row__block shopping">
               <span class="home__tips-title">Shopper Tips</span>
               <div class="owl-carousel home__tips-container">
                                       <div class="tip">
                        <span class="tip-title"> How to spot a counterfeit product (reactive)? </span>
                        <p class="tip-text"><p>Call 1729 hotline</p> </p>
                     </div>
                                       <div class="tip">
                        <span class="tip-title"> How to spot a counterfeit product (reactive)? </span>
                        <p class="tip-text"><p>Pay particular attention to the package and to any evidence of tampering.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> </p>
                     </div>
                                       <div class="tip">
                        <span class="tip-title"> How to spot a counterfeit product (reactive)? </span>
                        <p class="tip-text"><p>Check closely the spelling on the label, and look for mistakes especially in the brand &amp; logos design.&nbsp;</p> </p>
                     </div>
                                    <div class="clear"></div>
               </div>
            </div>
         
